Welcome to CRAK-2.6.25.6! The purpose of this module is 
to be able to checkpoint- and later restart- user level processes.

To properly build this module:
$> ./make build
- This invokes make config. This only need be done once.

Thereafter:
$> make modules
OR
$> make
will suffice!

To install the resulting module:
$> sudo ./ins

To remove the module:
$> sudo ./rmd

To test the module, refer to README in ./tests/ directory.

To produce documentation:
$> make docs

